    <item>
      <title>Temu 母公司 PDD 警告收入放缓，股价下跌 18%</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-26/temu-owner-pdd-s-sales-disappoint-after-global-expansion-slows</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在 Temu 所有者警告称收入增长将不可避免地放缓之后，拼多多控股有限公司 (PDD Holdings Inc.) 的股价一度暴跌 18%，凸显出在面对字节跳动有限公司 (ByteDance Ltd.) 等强劲竞争对手时维持扩张速度所面临的挑战。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-26/temu-owner-pdd-s-sales-disappoint-after-global-expansion-slows</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 26 Aug 2024 10:48:12 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>监管审查报告出炉后 Paytm 股价下跌</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-26/paytm-shares-drop-after-report-on-fresh-regulatory-scrutiny</link>
      <description><![CDATA[周一有消息称，印度市场监管机构已向 Paytm 创始人发出通知，指控其存在虚假陈述。Paytm 股价随后下跌。这家金融科技先驱表示，此举并非“新进展”。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-26/paytm-shares-drop-after-report-on-fresh-regulatory-scrutiny</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 26 Aug 2024 09:53:13 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
